data.description: Welcome to 103 Pooler Drive, Lafayette, a charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home boasting 1,840 sqft of comfortable living space. Nestled in a picturesque subdivision adorned with mature trees, this residence offers a tranquil ambiance complemented by a vast park area for leisurely activities. The Woodvale school district and easy interstate access enhance the convenience of this great location. The kitchen, featuring custom cabinets and granite countertops, is strategically positioned for easy cooking and an open flow to the rest of the house. Revel in the beauty of hardwood floors throughout, eliminating the need for carpeting.  This residence caters to diverse needs with three bedrooms, two bathrooms, and an additional living space off the kitchen, perfect for a breakfast nook, playroom, or sitting area. The presence of a sunlit office adds functionality and aesthetic appeal. Recent upgrades include a new AC, ductwork, electrical panel, and a roof approximately 6 years old. Ideal for a home business, the property even boasts a separate entrance from the carport. Enjoy privacy with a fully fenced backyard and the charming touch of a white picket fence in the front yard. This is an opportunity to embrace comfort, convenience, and versatility in one delightful home.
